Print the following pattern for the given number of rows.
Pattern for N = 5
E
DE
CDE
BCDE
ABCDE


Solution:

public class solution {

	public static void print(int n) {
        int i,j;
        char ch='A',c;
        ch = (char)(ch + n - 1);

        for (i = 1; i <= n; i++)
        {
            c=ch;
            for (j = 1; j<= i; j++)
            {
                System.out.print(c);
                c++;
            }
            ch--;
            System.out.println();
        }
    }
}
